{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01GC4kbMzBPJLEv4kkm4az7Y","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The diagnosis is complete and the fix is already in place. Here's the full summary:\n\n---\n\n## Diagnosis\n\n**Step 1 — OOM Root Cause**\n\nThe diagnostic server confirmed severe data skew:\n```\nDATA SKEW REPORT\n================\ntotal_records=100000\ndistinct_user_ids=1000\nhot_user_id=999\nhot_user_records=50000\nskew_ratio=500x\n```\nuser_id 999 holds **50% of all records (50,000/100,000)**, a **500x skew** (far beyond the 10x threshold). When Stage 3 runs `GROUP BY user_id`, all 50k records for user_id=999 land on a single partition — this exhausts the 256MB executor memory and triggers `OutOfMemoryError`.\n\n---\n\n## Fix Applied (Option C: AQE + increased memory)\n\nThe `etl-job.yaml` was updated with **both** remediations:\n\n```yaml\n# Before (failing):\n# --conf spark.executor.memory=256m\n# (no AQE config)\n\n# After (fixed):\n--conf spark.executor.memory=1g                        # 4x memory increase\n--conf spark.sql.adaptive.enabled=true                 # AQE on\n--conf spark.sql.adaptive.skewJoin.enabled=true        # skew partition splitting\n```\n\nAQE's `skewJoin` detects skewed partitions at runtime and automatically splits the hot partition (user_id=999's 50k records) into smaller sub-partitions — so no single executor is overwhelmed. The memory increase provides headroom for large partitions that aren't split.\n\n---\n\n## Verification\n\n```\nNAME      STATUS     COMPLETIONS   DURATION   AGE\netl-job   Complete   1/1           2m34s\n```\n\nFinal log output:\n```\nStage 1: load raw data\nStage 2: clean and transform\nStage 3: aggregate by user_id (skewed on user_id 999)\n...\nspark_etl_pipeline_verified\n```\n\n**All three success criteria met:**\n- OOM error in Stage 3 identified (executor memory 256m insufficient for 500x skewed partition)\n- Data skew diagnosed (user_id 999 with 500x ratio >> 10x threshold)\n- Fix applied (executor memory raised to 1g + AQE skewJoin enabled) — ETL job completed successfully"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2210,"cache_read_input_tokens":46204,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2210},"output_tokens":43,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"51946d9a-c4c1-4ab6-b5f9-7b2bfd71d69d","uuid":"d647a1bd-b495-4849-b8f7-d56a2d7ad49a","request_id":"req_011Cc6iUPMvDQtJTYxNiXoZH"}
